{"tid":1120233,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)洛奇拳王再臨 J神 VS Freddy 機械師 經期隊長","createTime":"2019-04-22T13:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T20:00:39.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"39ebe05e83dd255ae9608ea25b3fc9c812e6b948","tid":1120233,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T13:31:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0tmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=efd3e616\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0tmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=79ecab8f\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0tmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=14d7b012\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a>&lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/77/Rocky_Balboa_film_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F77%2FRocky_Balboa_film_poster.jpg&h=0bbbf351&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://images2.fanpop.com/images/photos/2800000/Freddy-vs-Jason-freddy-krueger-2835423-1280-1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages2.fanpop.com%2Fimages%2Fphotos%2F2800000%2FFreddy-vs-Jason-freddy-krueger-2835423-1280-1024.jpg&h=3dad5c57&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.char.tw/uploads/20190306062205_61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.char.tw%2Fuploads%2F20190306062205_61.jpg&h=47c9dabf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://kalselpos.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Captain-Marvel-001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkalselpos.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2FCaptain-Marvel-001.jpg&h=f3821f0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://joseph-morris.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/captain-marvel-gif-7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjoseph-morris.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2Fcaptain-marvel-gif-7.gif&h=3930e186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.傳奇的拳王洛奇早已全面退休，闊別拳壇多年，其妻子因病離世，失去了精神依靠的他，寄情經營以妻子的名字&quot;Adrian&quot;為名的餐廳為生。洛奇憑著響亮的名氣，吸引許多食客慕名而來，他每天在餐廳裡高談闊論過往大小戰蹟，已成為其生活重心。洛奇心中唯一寄託是已長大了的兒子&mdash;&mdash;勞勃，但兒子卻因為父親響亮的名聲，為他帶來很大壓力，令兩人關係生疏..<br />\n<br />\n2.猛鬼街片中的主角變態殺手弗萊迪由於被人忘卻，沒有人記得他也就沒有人恐懼他，為了重獲力量，他找到了一個臭名昭著變態殺手，一個帶著冰球面具而且從來不開口說話的傑森(肯&middot;克辛格)，他喜歡用一把彎刀肢解小孩子， 弗萊迪利用他的特長進入傑森的夢中，利用傑森母親的形象控制他，命令他到榆樹街上殺人，這樣弗萊迪才能重新得到復生的力量，被喚醒的傑森來到榆樹街大開殺戒，當地陷入一片恐慌，以前的孩子們再次陷入弗萊迪的噩夢<br />\n<br />\n3.故事敘述一名職業殺手亞瑟&middot;畢夏（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）武力高強、手法乾淨俐落，在殺完人後會將死者看起來像意外、自殺或他殺的模樣..<br />\n<br />\n4.1995年，克里帝國星際部隊成員佛斯在首都哈拉星進行訓練，她困惑於被清除記憶而難以控制自身情緒及能量，所屬部隊指揮官楊羅格與克里AI統治者「至高智慧」因此不斷告誡教誨她。楊羅格的部隊受命前往邊境星球托法星，試圖尋找失蹤的克里人臥底，卻掉入敵對的史克魯爾人所設下的圈套。佛斯被史克魯爾人將軍塔洛斯擄走，楊羅格與其他成員被逼撤退。史克魯爾人在太空船內以記憶讀取裝置收集佛斯腦中的情報，使她回想起片段的零碎記憶。佛斯用超能力脫困成功並試圖逃離，最後她所乘的逃生艙被塔洛斯攻擊毀損，從太空墜至鄰近星球C-53（地球）<br />\n<br />\n9 35PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0tmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=0a02ab1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0tmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=bc3bd1a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4307b4ca31505cb43712b3b132b62a83d4434627","tid":1120233,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T13:32:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/90/Mechanic_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F90%2FMechanic_poster.jpg&h=a0cb3255&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35e25043f8672aa92a208031155de071c3aa6abf","tid":1120233,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T13:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4898f188843dbc53641715cd5d12c93178cffa3","tid":1120233,"uid":45830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T14:03:10.000Z","msg":"經期隊長???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8368811ac4375691a9ec009584a4ab8d076dcde","tid":1120233,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T14:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img